{"tid":2263455,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葛珮帆離題倡規管網台：「不雅言論影響下一代。」","createTime":"2020-10-30T02:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T04:22:18.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"9df89fcaa65ec01f2c67e35c5fd2dd8ef6d8fa28","tid":2263455,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TY-ju18sEqF4OYBNGvkc4W_ZAlU=/3621x2414/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L7XBN6RAMVAARCRPMLGZY24JX4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTY-ju18sEqF4OYBNGvkc4W_ZAlU%3D%2F3621x2414%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL7XBN6RAMVAARCRPMLGZY24JX4.JPG&h=a3aabb29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n立法會今討論《2019年廣播及電訊法例（修訂）條例草案》恢復二讀，民建聯葛珮帆把話題扯到並非條草案的網台規管，被立法會主席梁君彥指離題。本報記者攝<br />\n...<br />\n葛珮帆席間借題發揮，指網上電視台和電台不受任何規管，聲稱收到很多市民投訴，指這類網台主持人使用不雅言詞或者傳播仇恨言論，甚至鼓吹暴力和傳播假新聞和消息，成為「攬炒派」撕裂社會、誤導市民參與違法活動的手段。她擔心市民對社會事務的看法受到這些網台節目所影響，直接影響下一代，促請政府積極研究如何規管網台，規管內容及運作，維護廣播生態系統、國家安全等：「全世界都向緊呢個方向發展。」結果被梁君彥指離題。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/NJ6VHV4CXFFFJBJKACUOSEJ6WE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FNJ6VHV4CXFFFJBJKACUOSEJ6WE%2F&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KPbhcgmijv%2F0DJBpEVBRbRs%3D&h=1c044339\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FNJ6VHV4CXFFFJBJKACUOSEJ6WE%2F&h=4910c15e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/NJ6VHV4CXFFFJBJKACUOSEJ6WE/</a>"},{"pid":"94db455f36b9e8adf764e66a10b20098b50dbfef","tid":2263455,"uid":282549,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:16:21.000Z","msg":"不學無術呃飯食一樣影響下一代"},{"pid":"a7f62089efb6b44d3e8f2a593fbe003c92b5bdcf","tid":2263455,"uid":82938,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTim